{"tid":1385482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"都市日報:「外資」沽物業 上環樓全幢售","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:10.000Z","uid":80725,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc83e3b6e2068ff55678038efcfec0f504e406ab","tid":1385482,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"2019/07/30 (週二) 12:00上午<br />\n<br />\n「外資」沽物業 上環樓全幢售<br />\n<br />\n「反送中」爭議不息，其中上環更連續兩個周日發生嚴重衝突，嚇得「外資」亦撤退。澳門基金八方金融有限公司決定放售上環文咸東街柏廷坊全幢物業，以現狀及連現有租約出售，項目總建築面積約7.1萬呎，市場估算市值約18億元，9月13日截標。<br />\n<br />\n位於文咸東街22至26號的柏廷坊，離上環站僅1分鐘步程，毗鄰多幢甲級商廈，包括無限極廣場及信德中心等，地契年期為999年。世邦魏理仕香港資本市場部主管及執行董事甄浚岷透露，近日接獲業主通知放售，項目樓高24層，現時1至9樓為餐飲樓面，10樓及以上為寫字樓，總建築面積70,616呎，物業連同命名權，以現狀及連現有租約出售，市場估值約18億元。<br />\n據悉，八方金融有限公司透過海外註冊公司，於三年前向建生國際(224)購入物業，當時作價10億元。假設以18億元成功沽出，平均呎價達2.55萬元，短短三年間帳面升值80%或8億元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019-07-29_22-35-55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F2019-07-29_22-35-55.jpg&h=742eab93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n柏廷坊位置便利，距離上環站僅1分鐘步程。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E3%80%8D%E6%B2%BD%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E6%A8%93%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%A2%E5%94%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A2%25E5%2594%25AE%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=4686e4b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E3%80%8D%E6%B2%BD%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E6%A8%93%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%A2%E5%94%AE/</a>"},{"pid":"27753a2ff64634c281a462a2cc4f4537d4c831f5","tid":1385482,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3a99ddb5bd3e666c915cfec9fd51052d0fe2c0","tid":1385482,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:10:53.000Z","msg":"樓價跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6931445f4184265c15034be8251cd12db48394","tid":1385482,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"澳門公司 睇落鬼鬼地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bd27b9d6615daf0d91910581f6dee8bdb27c4d","tid":1385482,"uid":291936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"咪ON9啦, 呢D 大DEAL 一傾傾幾個月, 點會係因此21/7 而令到佢成交。"}]}